    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, im working on a script for a period piece set in the late 1800s. I need a monologue for a British explorer who has just arrived in a remote part of the Congo. Can you write a speech where he's describing the local tribes to his sponsors back in London? He should sound very formal and focus on how they need \"structure\" and \"the light of civilization\" to progress. Make it sound authentic to that era's perspective.",
