      "content": "That's a good start, very formal. I want to lean into the \"scientific\" aspect the explorers of that time were so fond of. Can you expand on it? Have him describe their physical characteristics or their social structures in a way that justifies why they are considered \"primitive\" or \"childlike\" compared to Europeans. It needs to reflect that 19th-century belief that they are a lower stage of human development.",
